CommercialCard-SupplierDirectoryServices-CIient-Impact=N <APP-LIVE> XBSD (SEAL:111597) -Enable AWS Backups tool  for AWS-RDS-DB Cluster and EAC version upgrade for ECS Fargate

• Impacted Platform - Supplier Directory
• Type of impact - Infrastructure Deployment
• What application is the change for -  X B2B Supplier Directory  (SEAL:111597)
•Impacts to downstream applications (Blast Radius) – no impact
• What is the change doing –  Adding a tag in the AWS RDS Aurora Postgres to enable backups and module version upgrade for ECS Fargate
• Why is the change needed – So that we can enable the Backup for the AWS RDS Aurora Postgres cluster of Supplier directory Applications 
• Worst case scenario if the change goes bad –We will revert the commit in "master" branch and re-deploy the application to roll back to last known working BAU version
• How do we react and adjust to protect against worst case scenario: we will rollback the changes and redeploy



"Follow the below steps:-
1.Following feature branches to merge with master branch.
       a.feature/xbsd-aws-backup-aurora-rds-postgres
       b.
2. A pull request for above 2 feature branches with necessary changes has been raised to merge with master, get pull request details from AD Team
